spec |\n| `cli-toolkit/` | Dir | CLI toolkit design and spec |\n| `client-go/` | Dir | Generated Kubernetes client-go library |\n| `cmd/` | Dir | Go binaries (workload-manager, router, picod, etc.) |\n| `code-execution/` | Dir | Code execution design and spec |\n| `coverage.out` | File | Go coverage output |\n| `delta-spec.md` | File | Current delta spec (AR-029) |\n| `deployment/` | Dir | Deployment design, spec, and client-go docs |\n| `design.md` | File | Current design doc (AR-029) |\n| `go.mod` | File | Go module definition |\n| `go.sum` | File | Go module checksums |\n| `idle-cleanup/` | Dir | Idle cleanup design and spec |\n| `integrations/` | Dir | Integration design and spec |\n| `pkg/` | Dir | Go packages (apis, agentd, picod, workloadmanager, common) |\n| `project.md` | File | Project context document |\n| `proposal.md` | File | Current proposal (AR-028) |\n| `python-sdk/` | Dir | Python SDK (sdk-python) |\n| `sandbox-orchestration/` | Dir | Sandbox orchestration design and spec |\n| `session-routing/` | Dir | Session routing design and spec |\n| `session-store/` | Dir | Session store design and spec |\n| `tasks.md` | File | Root-level tasks file (for AR-023) |\n| `test_spec.md` | File | Test specification |\n| `testing/` | Dir | Testing utilities |\n\n---\n\n## 2. Manifests Directory Structure\n\n**There is NO `manifests/` directory currently in the project.** It does not exist at the top level or anywhere in the tree. The glob searches for `**/manifests/**` returned no results.\n\nHowever, the **design documents extensively reference** the intended structure at `manifests/charts/base/`. From `changes/AR-030/design.md` (lines 12-27):\n\n```\nmanifests/charts/base/\n├── Chart.yaml                              # Chart metadata\n├── values.yaml                             # Default configuration values\n├── crds/\n│   ├── runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_agentruntimes.yaml\n│   └── runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_codeinterpreters.yaml\n└── templates/\n    ├── work