d, proposal.md, tasks.md)\n├── ...\n├── AR-029/  (design.md, proposal.md, tasks.md)\n└── AR-030/  (delta-spec.md, design.md, proposal.md, tasks.md)\n```\n\nEach AR directory typically contains:\n- `proposal.md` -- Purpose, scope, impact analysis, alternatives considered\n- `design.md` -- Architecture, data structures, API contracts, error handling, testing strategy\n- `tasks.md` -- Implementation task breakdown with checkboxes\n- Some (like AR-030) also include `delta-spec.md`\n\n### Stage (ST) References\n\n**No standalone ST-*.md files exist** in the project. However, stages are referenced within tasks.md files:\n\n| Stage | Meaning | Referenced In |\n|-------|---------|---------------|\n| **ST-3** | Design Complete | AR-002 through AR-030 tasks.md files (all 27 references) |\n| **ST-4** | Implementation | AR-001 tasks.md |\n\nFrom `.sdd_prompt.md` (line 463): `[Stage ST-1 completed]` -- indicating ST-1 is also part of the lifecycle.\n\nThe stage convention in tasks.md headers is:\n- Early ARs (AR-002 to AR-012): `> **Stage**: ST-3 (Design Complete)`\n- Later ARs (AR-013 to AR-030): `> **Precondition:** Stage ST-3 (Design) completed`\n\n---\n\n## 7. Design Documents Related to ST-3 and AR-030\n\n### AR-030 Files (all under `changes/AR-030/`):\n\n1. **`proposal.md`** (117 lines)\n   - Module: manifests, Language: YAML, Size: L\n   - Purpose: Complete Helm chart for AgentCube control-plane stack\n   - Scope: Chart.yaml, values.yaml, templates for WM, Router, Volcano, RBAC, CRDs\n   - Out of scope: Dockerfiles, Makefile targets, E2E infrastructure, Python SDK, CLI\n\n2. **`design.md`** (798 lines) -- Extremely detailed, covering:\n   - Architecture: Package layout, dependencies, component deployment shape, code generation toolchain\n   - Data Structures: Chart.yaml metadata, complete values.yaml key tree, template variable mapping, RBAC rules, CRD definitions, Volcano ConfigMap structure\n   - API Contracts: Helm install commands (minimal, E2E, full), template rendering contracts, conditional rendering, naming conventions, imagePullSecrets\n   - Error Handling: Template errors, install-time validation, runtime errors (health probes, Redis, WM URL), upgrade errors, default/empty value handling\n   - Testing Strategy: Helm lint, template rendering tests (17+ scenarios), CRD validation, kubectl dry-run, test file layout, delta spec coverage matrix (50+ scenarios)\n   - Implementation Steps: File creation order, parallelization groups, verification checklist\n   - Follow-up Changes: CRD auto-generation, helm-unittest, apiVersion v2 upgrade, production values, Helm repo publishing, GitOps integration\n\n3. **`delta-spec.md`** (402 lines) -- Gherkin-style scenarios covering:\n   - Chart.yaml metadata validation\n   - values.yaml default key tree (5 scenarios)\n   - Workload Manager Deployment template (11 scenarios)\n   - Workload Manager Service template (2 scenarios)\n   - Router Deployment template (8 scenarios)\n   - Router Service template (1 scenario)\n   - Workload Manager RBAC template (6 scenarios)\n   - Optional Router RBAC template (4 scenarios)\n   - Optional Volcano scheduler template (6 scenarios)\n   - CRDs shipped with chart (4 scenarios)\n   - Helm install commands (3 scenarios)\n   - Helm upgrade preservation (2 scenarios)\n   - Template dry-run validation (2 scenarios)\n   - Namespace scoping (2 scenarios)\n   - nameOverride/fullnameOverride (2 scenarios)\n   - File changes table (9 files to create)\n\n4. **`tasks.md`** (39 lines) -- TODO template, not yet populated with actual tasks\n\n### ST-3 References\n\nST-3 (Design Complete) is referenced as a precondition in 27 tasks.md files (AR-002 through AR-030). It appears to be the stage where all design documents (design.md, proposal.md, delta-spec.md) are completed before implementation tasks begin.\n\n---\n\n## Summary\n\n| Search Target | Result |\n|---------------|--------|\n| `manifests/` directory | **Does not exist** -- planned but not yet created |\n| `**/helm/**` | No matches |\n| `**/charts/**` | No matches |\n| `**/templates/**` | No matches |\n| `**/values*.yaml` | No matches |\n| `**/Chart.yaml` | No matches |\n| `**/tasks.md` | **31 files** (root + 30 under changes/AR-*/ ) |\n| `**/AR-*.md` | No standalone AR-*.md files; AR content is in `changes/AR-NNN/` directories |\n| `**/ST-*.md` | No standalone ST-*.md files; stages referenced inline in tasks.md headers |\n| ST-3 references | **27 occurrences** across tasks.md files (precondition for implementation) |\n| AR-030 design docs | **4 files** under `changes/AR-030/`: proposal.md, design.md, delta-spec.md, tasks.md |\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_285d9347cffe4rXapQSAj7HaV2","model":{"modelID":"qwen3.6-plus","providerID":"alibaba-cn"},"truncated":false},"title":"Explore agentcube project structure","time":{"start":1775870856064,"end":1775870997835}}}}
