{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775871001423,"sessionID":"ses_285d94d8fffeNOnrGGHJVfF0qU","part":{"id":"prt_d7a28ff15001Fia5im8UmXOwLn","messageID":"msg_d7a28f59c001xaYdOcRgV6cI4S","sessionID":"ses_285d94d8fffeNOnrGGHJVfF0qU","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_5cb781817c7c4344b0306b56","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-030/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-030/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-030: Helm Chart 模板与 Values — Design/设计说明\n2: \n3: ## 1. 架构 (Architecture)\n4: \n5: ### 1.1 定位 (Purpose/Positioning)\n6: \n7: `manifests/charts/base` 是 AgentCube 控制面栈的 Helm Chart，提供参数化的 Kubernetes 资源模板，支持一键安装、升级和回滚。Chart 驱动 Workload Manager、Router、可选 Volcano 调度器的完整部署生命周期，通过 `values.yaml` 集中管理所有可配置参数（镜像、副本数、资源配额、Redis 连接、环境变量覆盖）。\n8: \n9: Chart 是 E2E 测试、生产部署、开发者本地 Kind 集群的统一入口，消除手动编辑 YAML 的需求。\n10: \n11: ### 1.2 包结构 (Package Layout)\n12: \n13: ```\n14: manifests/charts/base/\n15: ├── Chart.yaml                              # Chart 元数据 (apiVersion v1, name agentcube, version 0.1.0)\n16: ├── values.yaml                             # 默认配置值树 (Redis, Router, WorkloadManager, Volcano)\n17: ├── crds/\n18: │   ├── runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_agentruntimes.yaml    # AgentRuntime CRD (v1alpha1, Namespaced)\n19: │   └── runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_codeinterpreters.yaml # CodeInterpreter CRD (v1alpha1, Namespaced)\n20: └── templates/\n21:     ├── workloadmanager.yaml                # WM Deployment + Service\n22:     ├── agentcube-router.yaml               # Router Deployment + Service\n23:     ├── rbac/\n24:     │   └── workloadmanager.yaml            # WM ServiceAccount + ClusterRole + ClusterRoleBinding\n25:     ├── rbac-router.yaml                    # 可选 Router ServiceAccount + Role + RoleBinding\n26:     └── volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml  # 可选 Volcano 调度器全套资源\n27: ```\n28: \n29: ### 1.3 依赖关系 (Dependencies)\n30: \n31: ```\n32: Helm Chart (manifests/charts/base)\n33:   ├── 外部依赖\n34:   │   ├── Helm 3                          # Chart 打包与安装\n35:   │   ├── Kubernetes 1.28+                # CRD 注册、Deployment/Service/RBAC 创建\n36:   │   ├── Redis/Valkey (外部实例)          # 地址和密码通过 values 提供\n37:   │   └── agent-sandbox CRDs (外部)        # WM ClusterRole 引用 agents.x-k8s.io API group\n38:   │\n39:   ├── 构建产物依赖\n40:   │   ├── make gen-crd                    # 产出 manifests/charts/base/crds/*.yaml\n41:   │   ├── docker-build                    # workloadmanager 镜像\n42:   │   ├── docker-build-router             # agentcube-router 镜像\n43:   │   └── docker-build-picod              # picod 镜像 (sandbox 内使用)\n44:   │\n45:   ├──→ helm template                      渲染所有模板为 Kubernetes YAML\n46:   ├──→ helm upgrade --install             安装/升级到目标集群\n47:   ├──→ kubectl apply --dry-run=client     验证渲染结果有效性\n48:   └──→ test/e2e/run_e2e.sh               E2E 测试通过 helm install 部署\n49: ```\n50: \n51: ### 1.4 组件部署形态 (Component Deployment Shape)\n52: \n53: | 组件 | Kind | Service | Port | Health Endpoint | 条件渲染 |\n54: |------|------|---------|------|-----------------|----------|\n55: | Workload Manager | Deployment + Service | `workloadmanager` | 8080 | `GET /health` (liveness 10s, readiness 5s) | 始终渲染 |\n56: | Router | Deployment + Service | `agentcube-router` | 8080 | `GET /health/live` + `/health/ready` (1s initial, 2s period) | 始终渲染 |\n57: | Volcano Scheduler | Deployment + Service | `volcano-agent-scheduler-service` | 8080 | — | `volcano.scheduler.enabled` |\n58: | WM RBAC | SA + ClusterRole + ClusterRoleBinding | — | — | — | 始终渲染 |\n59: | Router RBAC | SA + Role + RoleBinding | — | — | — | `router.rbac.create` |\n60: \n61: ### 1.5 代码生成工具链 (Code Generation Toolchain)\n62: \n63: | 工具 | 版本 | 用途 |\n64: |------|------|------|\n65: | controller-gen | v0.17.2 | 从 Go 类型 kubebuilder 标记生成 CRD YAML 到 `manifests/charts/base/crds/` |\n66: | Helm | 3.x | Chart 模板渲染、安装、升级、回滚 |\n67: \n68: CRD 生成入口：`make gen-crd` → `controller-gen crd paths=./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/... output:crd:dir=manifests/charts/base/crds`。\n69: \n70: ---\n71: \n72: ## 2. 数据结构 (Data Structures)\n73: \n74: ### 2.1 Chart.yaml 元数据\n75: \n76: | 字段 | 值 | 说明 |\n77: |------|-----|------|\n78: | `apiVersion` | `v1` | Helm 3 兼容，当前 scope 无需 v2 |\n79: | `name` | `agentcube` | Chart 名称 |\n80: | `description` | `A Helm chart for AgentCube` | 简短描述 |\n81: | `version` | `0.1.0` | Chart 语义化版本 |\n82: | `appVersion` | `1.0.0` | 应用版本 |\n83: \n84: ### 2.2 values.yaml 完整键树\n85: \n86: ```yaml\n87: # imagePullSecrets — 私有镜像仓库认证\n88: imagePullSecrets: []\n89: # nameOverride — 覆盖 chart 名称用于资源命名\n90: nameOverride: \"\"\n91: # fullnameOverride — 完全覆盖资源名称前缀\n92: fullnameOverride: \"\"\n93: \n94: # Redis/Valkey 连接配置\n95: # 注意: 以下两个值必须在安装时通过 --set 提供\n96: redis:\n97:   addr: \"\"       # Redis 地址, 例: redis.agentcube.svc.cluster.local:6379\n98:   password: \"\"   # Redis 密码, 可为空字符串\n99: \n100: # Router 组件配置\n101: router:\n102:   replicas: 1\n103:   image:\n104:     repository: ghcr.io/volcano-sh/agentcube-router\n105:     pullPolicy: IfNotPresent\n106:     tag: latest\n107:   service:\n108:     type: ClusterIP\n109:     port: 8080\n110:     targetPort: 8080\n111:   resources:\n112:     limits:\n113:       cpu: 500m\n114:       memory: 512Mi\n115:     requests:\n116:       cpu: 100m\n117:       memory: 128Mi\n118:   config: {}\n119:   extraEnv: []\n120:   serviceAccountName: \"\"\n121:   rbac:\n122:     create: false\n123: \n124: # Workload Manager 组件配置\n125: workloadmanager:\n126:   replicas: 1\n127:   image:\n128:     repository: ghcr.io/volcano-sh/workloadmanager\n129:     pullPolicy: IfNotPresent\n130:     tag: latest\n131:   service:\n132:     type: ClusterIP\n133:     port: 8080\n134:   resources:\n135:     limits:\n136:       cpu: 500m\n137:       memory: 512Mi\n138:     requests:\n139:       cpu: 100m\n140:       memory: 128Mi\n141:   extraEnv: []\n142: \n143: # Volcano 调度器配置 (可选)\n144: volcano:\n145:   scheduler:\n146:     enabled: false\n147:     replicas: 1\n148:     image:\n149:       repository: ghcr.io/volcano-sh/vc-agent-scheduler\n150:       pullPolicy: IfNotPresent\n151:       tag: latest\n152: ```\n153: \n154: ### 2.3 values.yaml 键树关系图\n155: \n156: ```\n157: values.yaml\n158: ├── imagePullSecrets: []                  # 全局: 镜像拉取密钥\n159: ├── nameOverride: \"\"                      # 全局: 名称覆盖\n160: ├── fullnameOverride: \"\"                  # 全局: 全名覆盖\n161: ├── redis\n162: │   ├── addr: \"\"                          # 必填: Redis 地址 (安装时提供)\n163: │   └── password: \"\"                      # 可选: Redis 密码\n164: ├── router\n165: │   ├── replicas: 1                       # 副本数\n166: │   ├── image\n167: │   │   ├── repository: ghcr.io/volcano-sh/agentcube-router\n168: │   │   ├── pullPolicy: IfNotPresent\n169: │   │   └── tag: latest\n170: │   ├── service\n171: │   │   ├── type: ClusterIP\n172: │   │   ├── port: 8080\n173: │   │   └── targetPort: 8080\n174: │   ├── resources\n175: │   │   ├── limits: {cpu: 500m, memory: 512Mi}\n176: │   │   └── requests: {cpu: 100m, memory: 128Mi}\n177: │   ├── config: {}                        # 预留配置对象\n178: │   ├── extraEnv: []                      # 额外环境变量\n179: │   ├── serviceAccountName: \"\"            # 可选 SA 名称\n180: │   └── rbac\n181: │       └── create: false                 # 是否创建 Router RBAC\n182: ├── workloadmanager\n183: │   ├── replicas: 1\n184: │   ├── image\n185: │   │   ├── repository: ghcr.io/volcano-sh/workloadmanager\n186: │   │   ├── pullPolicy: IfNotPresent\n187: │   │   └── tag: latest\n188: │   ├── service\n189: │   │   ├── type: ClusterIP\n190: │   │   └── port: 8080\n191: │   ├── resources\n192: │   │   ├── limits: {cpu: 500m, memory: 512Mi}\n193: │   │   └── requests: {cpu: 100m, memory: 128Mi}\n194: │   └── extraEnv: []\n195: └── volcano\n196:     └── scheduler\n197:         ├── enabled: false                # 是否启用 Volcano 调度器\n198:         ├── replicas: 1\n199:         └── image\n200:             ├── repository: ghcr.io/volcano-sh/vc-agent-scheduler\n201:             ├── pullPolicy: IfNotPresent\n202:             └── tag: latest\n203: ```\n204: \n205: ### 2.4 模板变量映射 (Template Variable Mapping)\n206: \n207: #### 2.4.1 环境变量注入矩阵\n208: \n209: | 组件 | 环境变量 | 来源 | 模板表达式 |\n210: |------|----------|------|-----------|\n211: | Workload Manager | `AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE` | Pod 元数据 | `fieldRef: metadata.namespace` |\n212: | Workload Manager | `REDIS_ADDR` | values | `{{ .Values.redis.addr }}` |\n213: | Workload Manager | `REDIS_PASSWORD` | values | `{{ .Values.redis.password }}` |\n214: | Workload Manager | `extraEnv[*]` | values | `{{- range .Values.workloadmanager.extraEnv }}` |\n215: | Router | `AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE` | Pod 元数据 | `fieldRef: metadata.namespace` |\n216: | Router | `REDIS_ADDR` | values | `{{ .Values.redis.addr }}` |\n217: | Router | `REDIS_PASSWORD` | values | `{{ .Values.redis.password }}` |\n218: | Router | `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL` | 自动推导 | `http://workloadmanager.{{ .Release.Namespace }}.svc.cluster.local:{{ .Values.workloadmanager.service.port }}` |\n219: | Router | `extraEnv[*]` | values | `{{- range .Values.router.extraEnv }}` |\n220: | Volcano | `AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE` | Pod 元数据 | `fieldRef: metadata.namespace` |\n221: \n222: #### 2.4.2 容器参数映射\n223: \n224: | 组件 | 参数 | 来源 | 模板表达式 |\n225: |------|------|------|-----------|\n226: | Workload Manager | `--port` | values | `--port={{ .Values.workloadmanager.service.port }}` |\n227: | Workload Manager | `--runtime-class-name=` | 硬编码 | `--runtime-class-name=` (空值) |\n228: | Router | `--port` | values | `--port={{ .Values.router.service.targetPort }}` |\n229: | Router | `--debug` | 硬编码 | `--debug` |\n230: | Volcano | `--scheduler-name=agent-scheduler` | 硬编码 | `--scheduler-name=agent-scheduler` |\n231: \n232: ### 2.5 RBAC 规则定义 (RBAC Rules)\n233: \n234: #### 2.5.1 ClusterRole `workloadmanager` (始终渲染)\n235: \n236: | apiGroups | resources | verbs | 说明 |\n237: |-----------|-----------|-------|------|\n238: | `agents.x-k8s.io` | `sandboxes` | `get,list,watch,create,update,patch,delete` | agent-sandbox 沙箱管理 |\n239: | `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io` | `sandboxclaims` | `get,list,watch,create,update,patch,delete` | 沙箱声明 |\n240: | `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io` | `sandboxtemplates` | `get,list,watch,create,update,patch,delete` | 沙箱模板 |\n241: | `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io` | `sandboxwarmpools` | `get,list,watch,create,update,patch,delete` | 沙箱预热池 |\n242: | `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io` | `sandboxwarmpools/status` | `get,update,patch` | 预热池状态 |\n243: | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` | `codeinterpreters` | `get,list,watch,create,update,patch,delete` | CodeInterpreter CRD |\n244: | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` | `codeinterpreters/status` | `get,update,patch` | CodeInterpreter 状态 |\n245: | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` | `codeinterpreters/finalizers` | `update` | CodeInterpreter finalizer |\n246: | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` | `agentruntimes` | `get,list,watch` | AgentRuntime CRD (只读) |\n247: | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` | `agentruntimes/status` | `update,patch` | AgentRuntime 状态 |\n248: | `\"\"` | `pods` | `get,list,watch` | Pod 查询 |\n249: | `\"\"` | `secrets` | `get,list,watch,create,update,patch,delete` | Secret 管理 |\n250: | `authentication.k8s.io` | `tokenreviews` | `create` | 认证 Token 审查 |\n251: \n252: #### 2.5.2 Role `router` (条件渲染: `router.rbac.create`)\n253: \n254: | apiGroups | resources | verbs | 说明 |\n255: |-----------|-----------|-------|------|\n256: | `\"\"` | `secrets` | `get,list,watch,create,update,patch,delete` | 命名空间级 Secret 管理 |\n257: \n258: #### 2.5.3 ClusterRole `volcano-agent-scheduler` (条件渲染: `volcano.scheduler.enabled`)\n259: \n260: | apiGroups | resources | verbs |\n261: |-----------|-----------|-------|\n262: | `apiextensions.k8s.io` | `customresourcedefinitions` | `create,get,list,watch,delete` |\n263: | `\"\"` | `events` | `create,list,watch,update,patch` |\n264: | `\"\"` | `pods` | `get,list,watch,patch,delete` |\n265: | `\"\"` | `pods/status` | `update` |\n266: | `\"\"` | `pods/binding` | `create` |\n267: | `\"\"` | `persistentvolumeclaims` | `list,watch,update` |\n268: | `\"\"` | `persistentvolumes` | `list,watch,update` |\n269: | `\"\"` | `namespaces,services,replicationcontrollers` | `list,watch,get` |\n270: | `\"\"` | `resourcequotas` | `list,watch` |\n271: | `\"\"` | `nodes` | `get,list,watch,update,patch` |\n272: | `storage.k8s.io` | `storageclasses,csinodes,csidrivers,csistoragecapacities,volumeattachments` | `list,watch` |\n273: | `policy` | `poddisruptionbudgets` | `list,watch` |\n274: | `scheduling.k8s.io` | `priorityclasses` | `get,list,watch` |\n275: | `scheduling.incubator.k8s.io`, `scheduling.volcano.sh` | `podgroups` | `list,watch,update` |\n276: | `\"\"` | `configmaps` | `get,list,watch,create,delete,update` |\n277: | `apps` | `daemonsets,replicasets,statefulsets` | `list,watch,get` |\n278: | `coordination.k8s.io` | `leases` | `get,create,update,watch` |\n279: | `resource.k8s.io` | `resourceclaims` | `get,list,watch,create,update,patch` |\n280: | `resource.k8s.io` | `resourceclaims/status` | `update` |\n281: | `resource.k8s.io` | `deviceclasses,resourceslices` | `get,list,watch,create` |\n282: | `shard.volcano.sh` | `nodeshards` | `list,watch,get,update` |\n283: \n284: ### 2.6 CRD 定义 (CRD Definitions)\n285: \n286: #### 2.6.1 AgentRuntime CRD\n287: \n288: | 属性 | 值 |\n289: |------|-----|\n290: | 文件名 | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_agentruntimes.yaml` |\n291: | CRD 名称 | `agentruntimes.runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` |\n292: | API Group | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` |\n293: | Version | `v1alpha1` (served + storage) |\n294: | Scope | `Namespaced` |\n295: | 注解 | `controller-gen.kubebuilder.io/version: v0.17.2` |\n296: | PrinterColumn | `Age` (date, `.metadata.creationTimestamp`) |\n297: | Subresources | `status` |\n298: | spec.required | `maxSessionDuration`, `podTemplate`, `sessionTimeout`, `targetPort` |\n299: \n300: **关键 spec 字段：**\n301: \n302: | 字段 | 类型 | 默认值 | 说明 |\n303: |------|------|--------|------|\n304: | `maxSessionDuration` | string (duration) | `8h` | 会话最大存活时间 |\n305: | `sessionTimeout` | string (duration) | `15m` | 会话空闲超时 |\n306: | `targetPort` | array of port objects | — | 端口列表 (required: `port`, `protocol` enum HTTP/HTTPS) |\n307: | `podTemplate` | object (PodSpec-shaped) | — | 沙箱 Pod 模板 (必填) |\n308: \n309: #### 2.6.2 CodeInterpreter CRD\n310: \n311: | 属性 | 值 |\n312: |------|-----|\n313: | 文件名 | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_codeinterpreters.yaml` |\n314: | CRD 名称 | `codeinterpreters.runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` |\n315: | API Group | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` |\n316: | Version | `v1alpha1` (served + storage) |\n317: | Scope | `Namespaced` |\n318: | 注解 | `controller-gen.kubebuilder.io/version: v0.17.2` |\n319: | Subresources | `status` |\n320: | spec.required | `template` |\n321: \n322: **关键 spec 字段：**\n323: \n324: | 字段 | 类型 | 默认值 | 说明 |\n325: |------|------|--------|------|\n326: | `authMode` | enum `picod\\|none` | `picod` | 认证模式 |\n327: | `maxSessionDuration` | string (duration) | `8h` | 会话最大存活时间 |\n328: | `sessionTimeout` | string (duration) | `15m` | 会话空闲超时 |\n329: | `ports` | array of TargetPort | — | 端口列表 |\n330: | `template` | object | — | 容器模板 (image, command, args, env, resources, runtimeClassName) |\n331: | `warmPoolSize` | int32 | — | 预热池大小 (可选) |\n332: \n333: ### 2.7 Volcano ConfigMap 结构\n334: \n335: ```yaml\n336: apiVersion: v1\n337: kind: ConfigMap\n338: metadata:\n339:   name: volcano-agent-scheduler-configmap\n340: data:\n341:   agent-scheduler.conf: |\n342:     actions: \"allocate\"\n343:     tiers:\n344:       - plugins:\n345:           - name: predicates\n346:           - name: nodeorder\n347: ```\n348: \n349: ---\n350: \n351: ## 3. API 契约 (API Contracts)\n352: \n353: ### 3.1 Helm 安装契约\n354: \n355: #### 3.1.1 最小安装命令\n356: \n357: ```bash\n358: helm upgrade --install agentcube manifests/charts/base \\\n359:   --namespace agentcube \\\n360:   --create-namespace \\\n361:   --set redis.addr=redis.agentcube.svc.cluster.local:6379 \\\n362:   --set redis.password=pass \\\n363:   --wait\n364: ```\n365: \n366: #### 3.1.2 E2E 测试安装命令 (Kind 集群)\n367: \n368: ```bash\n369: helm upgrade --install agentcube manifests/charts/base \\\n370:   --namespace \"${AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE}\" \\\n371:   --create-namespace \\\n372:   --set redis.addr=\"redis.${AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE}.svc.cluster.local:6379\" \\\n373:   --set redis.password=\"\" \\\n374:   --set workloadmanager.image.repository=\"workloadmanager\" \\\n375:   --set workloadmanager.image.tag=\"latest\" \\\n376:   --set-json 'workloadmanager.extraEnv=[{\"name\":\"REDIS_PASSWORD_REQUIRED\",\"value\":\"false\"},{\"name\":\"JWT_KEY_SECRET_NAMESPACE\",\"value\":\"agentcube\"}]' \\\n377:   --set router.image.repository=\"agentcube-router\" \\\n378:   --set router.image.tag=\"latest\" \\\n379:   --set router.rbac.create=true \\\n380:   --set router.serviceAccountName=\"agentcube-router\" \\\n381:   --set-json 'router.extraEnv=[{\"name\":\"REDIS_PASSWORD_REQUIRED\",\"value\":\"false\"}]' \\\n382:   --wait\n383: ```\n384: \n385: #### 3.1.3 完整功能安装命令\n386: \n387: ```bash\n388: helm upgrade --install agentcube manifests/charts/base \\\n389:   --namespace production \\\n390:   --create-namespace \\\n391:   --set redis.addr=redis.production.svc.cluster.local:6379 \\\n392:   --set redis.password=secret123 \\\n393:   --set workloadmanager.replicas=3 \\\n394:   --set workloadmanager.image.tag=v1.1.0 \\\n395:   --set router.replicas=2 \\\n396:   --set router.rbac.create=true \\\n397:   --set router.serviceAccountName=agentcube-router \\\n398:   --set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true \\\n399:   --set-json 'imagePullSecrets=[{\"name\":\"ghcr-pull-secret\"}]' \\\n400:   --set-json 'workloadmanager.extraEnv=[{\"name\":\"LOG_LEVEL\",\"value\":\"info\"}]' \\\n401:   --wait\n402: ```\n403: \n404: ### 3.2 模板渲染契约\n405: \n406: #### 3.2.1 命名空间作用域\n407: \n408: 所有命名空间级资源必须使用 `{{ .Release.Namespace }}` 作为 `metadata.namespace`，不得使用硬编码值：\n409: \n410: | 资源 | Namespace 来源 |\n411: |------|---------------|\n412: | Deployment/workloadmanager | `{{ .Release.Namespace }}` |\n413: | Service/workloadmanager | `{{ .Release.Namespace }}` |\n414: | ServiceAccount/workloadmanager | `{{ .Release.Namespace }}` |\n415: | Deployment/agentcube-router | `{{ .Release.Namespace }}` |\n416: | Service/agentcube-router | `{{ .Release.Namespace }}` |\n417: | ConfigMap/volcano-agent-scheduler-configmap | `{{ .Release.Namespace }}` |\n418: | Service/volcano-agent-scheduler-service | `{{ .Release.Namespace }}` |\n419: | Deployment/volcano-agent-scheduler | `{{ .Release.Namespace }}` |\n420: \n421: ClusterRole 和 ClusterRoleBinding 为集群级资源，无 namespace 字段。\n422: \n423: #### 3.2.2 资源选择器契约\n424: \n425: | Deployment | Service Selector |\n426: |------------|-----------------|\n427: | `workloadmanager` | `app: workloadmanager` |\n428: | `agentcube-router` | `app: agentcube-router` |\n429: | `volcano-agent-scheduler` | `app: volcano-agent-scheduler` |\n430: \n431: #### 3.2.3 容器端口命名\n432: \n433: | 组件 | 端口名 | 端口值 |\n434: |------|--------|--------|\n435: | Workload Manager | `http` | `{{ .Values.workloadmanager.service.port }}` |\n436: | Router | — | `{{ .Values.router.service.targetPort }}` |\n437: | Volcano | — | `8080` |\n438: \n439: ### 3.3 条件渲染契约\n440: \n441: | 模板 | 条件 | 渲染产物 |\n442: |------|------|----------|\n443: | `rbac-router.yaml` | `{{- if .Values.router.rbac.create }}` | ServiceAccount + Role + RoleBinding |\n444: | `volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml` | `{{- if .Values.volcano.scheduler.enabled }}` | ServiceAccount + ConfigMap + ClusterRole + ClusterRoleBinding + Service + Deployment |\n445: \n446: #### 3.3.1 Router RBAC 名称解析\n447: \n448: 当 `router.rbac.create` 为 true 时，所有 RBAC 资源名称为：\n449: ```\n450: {{ .Values.router.serviceAccountName | default \"agentcube-router\" }}\n451: ```\n452: \n453: #### 3.3.2 Router serviceAccountName 条件注入\n454: \n455: Router Deployment 的 `serviceAccountName` 仅在值非空时设置：\n456: ```yaml\n457: {{- if .Values.router.serviceAccountName }}\n458: serviceAccountName: {{ .Values.router.serviceAccountName }}\n459: {{- end }}\n460: ```\n461: \n462: ### 3.4 nameOverride / fullnameOverride 契约\n463: \n464: Chart 支持标准 Helm 命名覆盖模式：\n465: \n466: | 值 | 行为 |\n467: |----|------|\n468: | 默认 (空) | 资源使用组件固定名称 (`workloadmanager`, `agentcube-router`) |\n469: | `fullnameOverride` 非空 | 适用资源使用 `fullnameOverride` 作为名称前缀 |\n470: | `nameOverride` 非空 | 适用资源使用 `nameOverride` 作为名称覆盖 |\n471: \n472: 命名辅助函数 (推荐定义在 `_helpers.tpl` 中):\n473: ```\n474: {{- define \"agentcube.fullname\" -}}\n475: {{- if .Values.fullnameOverride }}\n476: {{- .Values.fullnameOverride | trunc 63 | trimSuffix \"-\" }}\n477: {{- else }}\n478: {{- $name := default .Chart.Name .Values.nameOverride }}\n479: {{- printf \"%s-%s\" .Release.Name $name | trunc 63 | trimSuffix \"-\" }}\n480: {{- end }}\n481: {{- end }}\n482: ```\n483: \n484: ### 3.5 imagePullSecrets 契约\n485: \n486: 当 `imagePullSecrets` 非空时，所有 Deployment 的 `spec.template.spec.imagePullSecrets` 应注入：\n487: ```yaml\n488: {{- with .Values.imagePullSecrets }}\n489: imagePullSecrets:\n490:   {{- toYaml . | nindent 2 }}\n491: {{- end }}\n492: ```\n493: \n494: ---\n495: \n496: ## 4. 错误处理 (Error Handling)\n497: \n498: ### 4.1 模板渲染错误\n499: \n500: | 场景 | 表现 | 处理方式 |\n501: |------|------|----------|\n502: | values.yaml 语法错误 | `helm template` 报错 YAML parse error | 安装前通过 `helm lint` 捕获 |\n503: | 模板语法错误 | `helm template` 报错 template rendering failed | 开发阶段通过 `helm template` dry-run 发现 |\n504: | 缺少必需 values | 渲染出空字符串 (如 `REDIS_ADDR=`) | values.yaml 注释标明必填；安装命令文档明确 `--set redis.addr=...` |\n505: | 类型不匹配 | Helm 类型转换失败 (如 string 用于 int 字段) | values.yaml 使用正确类型；`helm lint` 可检测部分问题 |\n506: \n507: ### 4.2 安装时验证错误\n508: \n509: | 场景 | Helm 行为 | 预期错误信息 |\n510: |------|----------|-------------|\n511: | CRD 已存在且 schema 不兼容 | `helm install` 失败 | `existing resource conflicts with existing CRD` |\n512: | RBAC 资源权限不足 | `helm install` 失败 | `clusterroles.rbac.authorization.k8s.io is forbidden` |\n513: | 命名空间不存在 (无 --create-namespace) | `helm install` 失败 | `namespaces \"xxx\" not found` |\n514: | 镜像拉取失败 | Pod 进入 `ImagePullBackOff` | 事件日志: `Failed to pull image` |\n515: \n516: ### 4.3 运行时错误处理\n517: \n518: #### 4.3.1 健康探针失败\n519: \n520: | 组件 | 探针 | 失败行为 |\n521: |------|------|----------|\n522: | Workload Manager | liveness `/health` (10s initial, 10s period) | 容器重启 |\n523: | Workload Manager | readiness `/health` (5s initial, 5s period) | 从 Service endpoints 移除 |\n524: | Router | liveness `/health/live` (1s initial, 2s period) | 容器重启 |\n525: | Router | readiness `/health/ready` (1s initial, 2s period) | 从 Service endpoints 移除 |\n526: \n527: #### 4.3.2 Redis 连接失败\n528: \n529: | 场景 | 影响 | 表现 |\n530: |------|------|------|\n531: | `redis.addr` 为空 | WM/Router 启动时无法连接 Redis | 健康探针失败 → 容器重启循环 |\n532: | `redis.password` 错误 | Redis 认证失败 | 日志显示 auth error；健康探针失败 |\n533: | Redis 服务不可达 | 会话存储不可用 | Router 无法路由会话；WM 无法管理沙箱状态 |\n534: \n535: #### 4.3.3 WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL 解析失败\n536: \n537: | 场景 | 影响 |\n538: |------|------|\n539: | Workload Manager Service 未就绪 | Router 无法转发请求 → 502/503 |\n540: | 命名空间不匹配 (多集群场景) | DNS 解析失败 → Router 启动异常 |\n541: \n542: ### 4.4 升级错误处理\n543: \n544: | 场景 | Helm 行为 | 恢复策略 |\n545: |------|----------|----------|\n546: | 新 values 导致模板渲染失败 | `helm upgrade` 回滚到上一版本 | 检查 `helm history`，修复 values 后重试 |\n547: | CRD schema 变更不兼容 | CRD 更新失败，其余资源可能已更新 | 手动回滚 CRD，`helm rollback` 恢复 |\n548: | 镜像 tag 不存在 | Pod 进入 `ImagePullBackOff` | `helm rollback` 或修正 image tag 后 `helm upgrade` |\n549: \n550: ### 4.5 默认值与空值处理\n551: \n552: | 字段 | 默认值 | 空值行为 |\n553: |------|--------|----------|\n554: | `redis.addr` | `\"\"` | 渲染为空字符串；容器启动失败 |\n555: | `redis.password` | `\"\"` | 渲染为空字符串；部分 Redis 实例允许无密码 |\n556: | `router.serviceAccountName` | `\"\"` | 不设置 `serviceAccountName` 字段 (使用 default SA) |\n557: | `router.rbac.create` | `false` | 不渲染 Router RBAC 资源 |\n558: | `volcano.scheduler.enabled` | `false` | 不渲染 Volcano 相关资源 |\n559: | `workloadmanager.extraEnv` | `[]` | 不注入额外环境变量 |\n560: | `router.extraEnv` | `[]` | 不注入额外环境变量 |\n561: | `imagePullSecrets` | `[]` | 不设置 `imagePullSecrets` 字段 |\n562: \n563: ---\n564: \n565: ## 5. 测试策略 (Testing Strategy)\n566: \n567: ### 5.1 静态验证 (Static Validation)\n568: \n569: #### 5.1.1 Helm Lint\n570: \n571: ```bash\n572: # 验证 chart 结构、values 类型、模板语法\n573: helm lint manifests/charts/base\n574: ```\n575: \n576: 预期输出：无 errors，允许 warnings（如 `icon` 字段缺失）。\n577: \n578: #### 5.1.2 YAML 语法验证\n579: \n580: ```bash\n581: # 验证 values.yaml 为合法 YAML\n582: python3 -c \"import yaml; yaml.safe_load(open('manifests/charts/base/values.yaml'))\"\n583: \n584: # 验证 Chart.yaml 为合法 YAML\n585: python3 -c \"import yaml; yaml.safe_load(open('manifests/charts/base/Chart.yaml'))\"\n586: ```\n587: \n588: ### 5.2 模板渲染测试 (Template Rendering Tests)\n589: \n590: #### 5.2.1 默认值渲染\n591: \n592: ```bash\n593: # 验证默认模板输出包含预期资源\n594: helm template test manifests/charts/base | grep -c \"kind: Deployment\"   # 期望: 2\n595: helm template test manifests/charts/base | grep -c \"kind: Service\"      # 期望: 2\n596: helm template test manifests/charts/base | grep -c \"kind: ClusterRole\"  # 期望: 1\n597: helm template test manifests/charts/base | grep -c \"kind: ServiceAccount\" # 期望: 1\n598: ```\n599: \n600: #### 5.2.2 关键场景渲染验证\n601: \n602: | 场景 | 命令 | 断言 |\n603: |------|------|------|\n604: | 默认 WM Deployment | `helm template test manifests/charts/base -s templates/workloadmanager.yaml` | `replicas: 1`, `image: ghcr.io/volcano-sh/workloadmanager:latest` |\n605: | Redis env 注入 | `helm template test manifests/charts/base --set redis.addr=redis.ns:6379 --set redis.password=secret` | 输出含 `REDIS_ADDR: redis.ns:6379` 和 `REDIS_PASSWORD: secret` |\n606: | WM 健康探针 | `helm template test manifests/charts/base -s templates/workloadmanager.yaml` | liveness `/health` initialDelay 10s, readiness `/health` initialDelay 5s |\n607: | Router WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL | `helm template test manifests/charts/base --namespace agentcube` | `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL=http://workloadmanager.agentcube.svc.cluster.local:8080` |\n608: | Router 健康探针 | `helm template test manifests/charts/base -s templates/agentcube-router.yaml` | liveness `/health/live` initialDelay 1s, readiness `/health/ready` initialDelay 1s |\n609: | 自定义副本数 | `helm template test manifests/charts/base --set workloadmanager.replicas=3` | `replicas: 3` |\n610: | 自定义镜像 | `helm template test manifests/charts/base --set workloadmanager.image.repository=myregistry/wm --set workloadmanager.image.tag=v1.2.3` | `image: myregistry/wm:v1.2.3` |\n611: | extraEnv 注入 | `helm template test manifests/charts/base --set-json 'workloadmanager.extraEnv=[{\"name\":\"CUSTOM\",\"value\":\"val\"}]'` | 输出含 `CUSTOM: val` |\n612: | Router RBAC 关闭 | `helm template test manifests/charts/base` | 无 Router SA/Role/RoleBinding |\n613: | Router RBAC 开启 | `helm template test manifests/charts/base --set router.rbac.create=true` | 输出含 Router SA + Role + RoleBinding |\n614: | Volcano 关闭 | `helm template test manifests/charts/base` | 无 Volcano 资源 |\n615: | Volcano 开启 | `helm template test manifests/charts/base --set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true` | 输出含 Volcano SA + ConfigMap + ClusterRole + CRB + Service + Deployment |\n616: | imagePullSecrets | `helm template test manifests/charts/base --set-json 'imagePullSecrets=[{\"name\":\"my-secret\"}]'` | `imagePullSecrets: [{name: my-secret}]` |\n617: | 命名空间作用域 | `helm template test manifests/charts/base --namespace production` | 所有命名空间资源 `namespace: production` |\n618: \n619: #### 5.2.3 CRD 渲染验证\n620: \n621: ```bash\n622: # 验证 CRD 包含在模板输出中\n623: helm template test manifests/charts/base --include-crds | grep \"kind: CustomResourceDefinition\"\n624: \n625: # 验证 AgentRuntime CRD\n626: helm template test manifests/charts/base --include-crds | grep \"agentruntimes.runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"\n627: \n628: # 验证 CodeInterpreter CRD\n629: helm template test manifests/charts/base --include-crds | grep \"codeinterpreters.runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"\n630: ```\n631: \n632: ### 5.3 Kubernetes 验证 (Dry-Run)\n633: \n634: ```bash\n635: # 默认值 dry-run 验证\n636: helm template test manifests/charts/base | kubectl apply --dry-run=client -f -\n637: \n638: # 全量 overrides dry-run 验证\n639: helm template test manifests/charts/base \\\n640:   --set redis.addr=redis.ns.svc:6379 \\\n641:   --set redis.password=secret \\\n642:   --set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true \\\n643:   --set router.rbac.create=true \\\n644:   | kubectl apply --dry-run=client -f -\n645: ```\n646: \n647: ### 5.4 测试文件布局\n648: \n649: ```\n650: manifests/charts/base/\n651: ├── Chart.yaml\n652: ├── values.yaml\n653: ├── crds/\n654: │   ├── runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_agentruntimes.yaml\n655: │   └── runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_codeinterpreters.yaml\n656: └── templates/\n657:     ├── workloadmanager.yaml\n658:     ├── agentcube-router.yaml\n659:     ├── rbac/\n660:     │   └── workloadmanager.yaml\n661:     ├── rbac-router.yaml\n662:     └── volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml\n663: \n664: test/chart/                          # Chart 测试脚本 (可选)\n665: ├── test_values.sh                   # values.yaml 结构验证\n666: ├── test_render.sh                   # 模板渲染场景测试\n667: └── test_crd.sh                      # CRD 验证\n668: ```\n669: \n670: ### 5.5 测试运行命令\n671: \n672: ```bash\n673: # 1. Lint\n674: helm lint manifests/charts/base\n675: \n676: # 2. 模板渲染验证\n677: helm template test manifests/charts/base > /tmp/agentcube-rendered.yaml\n678: \n679: # 3. 客户端 dry-run (需要 kubectl 和集群连接)\n680: kubectl apply --dry-run=client -f /tmp/agentcube-rendered.yaml\n681: \n682: # 4. E2E 集成测试 (需要 Kind 集群)\n683: make e2e   # 内部调用 test/e2e/run_e2e.sh，包含 helm install 验证\n684: ```\n685: \n686: ### 5.6 Delta Spec 场景覆盖矩阵\n687: \n688: | Delta Spec 场景 | 测试方法 | 验证点 |\n689: |-----------------|----------|--------|\n690: | Chart metadata fields | `helm lint` + YAML parse | apiVersion=v1, name=agentcube, version=0.1.0, appVersion=1.0.0 |\n691: | Default values valid YAML | YAML parse | 所有顶层键存在 |\n692: | Redis defaults empty strings | values.yaml 读取 | addr=\"\", password=\"\", 含注释 |\n693: | Router defaults match design | values.yaml 读取 | replicas=1, repo/pullPolicy/tag/service/resources/rbac 全部匹配 |\n694: | WM defaults match design | values.yaml 读取 | replicas=1, repo/pullPolicy/tag/service/resources 全部匹配 |\n695: | Volcano disabled by default | values.yaml 读取 | enabled=false |\n696: | Default WM deployment renders | `helm template` | Deployment name, replicas, image, pullPolicy |\n697: | WM health probes | `helm template` | liveness/readiness paths and timings |\n698: | Redis env vars injected | `helm template --set` | REDIS_ADDR, REDIS_PASSWORD in env |\n699: | AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE fieldRef | `helm template` | valueFrom.fieldRef.fieldPath: metadata.namespace |\n700: | extraEnv appended | `helm template --set-json` | custom env vars present |\n701: | Container args port+runtime | `helm template` | --port=8080, --runtime-class-name= |\n702: | Resource requests/limits | `helm template` | requests/limits match values |\n703: | Custom replica count | `helm template --set` | replicas updated |\n704: | Custom image override | `helm template --set` | image updated |\n705: | imagePullSecrets applied | `helm template --set-json` | imagePullSecrets in pod spec |\n706: | Default WM service renders | `helm template` | type/port/targetPort/selector |\n707: | Custom service type | `helm template --set` | service type updated |\n708: | Default router deployment | `helm template` | Deployment name, replicas, image |\n709: | WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL DNS | `helm template --namespace` | URL with correct namespace and port |\n710: | Router health probes | `helm template` | /health/live, /health/ready timings |\n711: | Router args port+debug | `helm template` | --port=8080, --debug |\n712: | Conditional serviceAccountName | `helm template --set` | SA name set when non-empty |\n713: | Empty serviceAccountName omitted | `helm template` | no serviceAccountName field |\n714: | Router extraEnv | `helm template --set-json` | custom env vars present |\n715: | Default router service | `helm template` | type/port/targetPort/selector |\n716: | WM RBAC ServiceAccount | `helm template` | SA in release namespace |\n717: | WM ClusterRole sandbox CRDs | `helm template` | agents.x-k8s.io rules |\n718: | WM ClusterRole AgentCube CRDs | `helm template` | runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh rules |\n719: | WM ClusterRole status/finalizers | `helm template` | status/finalizer verbs |\n720: | WM ClusterRole secrets+tokenreview | `helm template` | secrets full verbs, tokenreviews create |\n721: | ClusterRoleBinding ties SA | `helm template` | subject and roleRef correct |\n722: | Router RBAC off by default | `helm template` | no Router RBAC resources |\n723: | Router RBAC enabled | `helm template --set` | SA+Role+RoleBinding present |\n724: | Router RBAC custom SA name | `helm template --set` | resources named with custom SA |\n725: | Router Role secret management | `helm template --set` | secrets full verbs |\n726: | Volcano disabled by default | `helm template` | no Volcano resources |\n727: | Volcano enabled | `helm template --set` | SA+ConfigMap+CR+CRB+Service+Deployment |\n728: | Volcano ConfigMap config | `helm template --set` | agent-scheduler.conf with allocate/predicates/nodeorder |\n729: | Volcano Deployment replicas+image | `helm template --set` | replicas and image match values |\n730: | Volcano Deployment args | `helm template --set` | --scheduler-name=agent-scheduler |\n731: | Volcano Service metrics | `helm template --set` | port 8080, prometheus annotations |\n732: | AgentRuntime CRD present | `helm template --include-crds` | CRD name, group, version, scope |\n733: | CodeInterpreter CRD present | `helm template --include-crds` | CRD name, group, version, scope |\n734: | AgentRuntime required fields | CRD YAML parse | spec.required includes maxSessionDuration, podTemplate, sessionTimeout, targetPort |\n735: | CodeInterpreter required fields | CRD YAML parse | spec.required includes template, authMode default picod |\n736: | Namespace scoping | `helm template --namespace` | all namespaced resources use correct namespace |\n737: | Default naming convention | `helm template` | resource names follow chart defaults |\n738: | fullnameOverride | `helm template --set` | resource names use override value |\n739: \n740: ---\n741: \n742: ## 6. 实现步骤 (Implementation Steps)\n743: \n744: ### 6.1 文件创建顺序\n745: \n746: 1. `manifests/charts/base/Chart.yaml` — Chart 元数据 (无依赖)\n747: 2. `manifests/charts/base/values.yaml` — 默认值树 (无依赖)\n748: 3. `manifests/charts/base/crds/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_agentruntimes.yaml` — AgentRuntime CRD (依赖 `make gen-crd` 或手工编写)\n749: 4. `manifests/charts/base/crds/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_codeinterpreters.yaml` — CodeInterpreter CRD (依赖 `make gen-crd` 或手工编写)\n750: 5. `manifests/charts/base/templates/workloadmanager.yaml` — WM Deployment + Service (依赖 values.yaml)\n751: 6. `manifests/charts/base/templates/agentcube-router.yaml` — Router Deployment + Service (依赖 values.yaml)\n752: 7. `manifests/charts/base/templates/rbac/workloadmanager.yaml` — WM RBAC (无依赖)\n753: 8. `manifests/charts/base/templates/rbac-router.yaml` — 可选 Router RBAC (依赖 values.yaml)\n754: 9. `manifests/charts/base/templates/volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml` — 可选 Volcano (依赖 values.yaml)\n755: \n756: ### 6.2 并行化分组\n757: \n758: | 组 | 任务 | 前置条件 |\n759: |----|------|----------|\n760: | G1 | Chart.yaml, values.yaml | 无 |\n761: | G2 | CRD 文件 (2 个) | G1 完成 (目录存在)；或 `make gen-crd` |\n762: | G3 | workloadmanager.yaml, agentcube-router.yaml | G1 完成 (values.yaml 结构确定) |\n763: | G4 | rbac/workloadmanager.yaml, rbac-router.yaml, volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml | G1 完成 |\n764: \n765: ### 6.3 验证检查清单\n766: \n767: - [ ] `helm lint manifests/charts/base` 无 errors\n768: - [ ] `helm template test manifests/charts/base` 输出合法 YAML\n769: - [ ] `helm template test manifests/charts/base | kubectl apply --dry-run=client -f -` 无验证错误\n770: - [ ] Chart.yaml: apiVersion=v1, name=agentcube, version=0.1.0, appVersion=1.0.0\n771: - [ ] values.yaml: 所有顶层键存在 (imagePullSecrets, nameOverride, fullnameOverride, redis, router, workloadmanager, volcano)\n772: - [ ] values.yaml: redis.addr 和 redis.password 默认为 `\"\"`，含安装时必填注释\n773: - [ ] WM Deployment: replicas, image, pullPolicy, port, env (AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE fieldRef, REDIS_ADDR, REDIS_PASSWORD, extraEnv), args (--port, --runtime-class-name=), resources, probes, serviceAccountName\n774: - [ ] WM Service: type, port, targetPort, selector app:workloadmanager\n775: - [ ] Router Deployment: replicas, conditional serviceAccountName, image, port, env (含 WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL), args (--port, --debug), resources, probes\n776: - [ ] Router Service: type, port, targetPort, selector app:agentcube-router\n777: - [ ] WM RBAC: SA + ClusterRole (完整规则集) + ClusterRoleBinding\n778: - [ ] Router RBAC: 条件渲染，SA + Role (secrets 全权限) + RoleBinding\n779: - [ ] Volcano: 条件渲染，SA + ConfigMap + ClusterRole + ClusterRoleBinding + Service + Deployment\n780: - [ ] CRDs: AgentRuntime + CodeInterpreter 在 crds/ 目录下，group/version/scope 正确\n781: - [ ] 命名空间: 所有命名空间资源使用 `{{ .Release.Namespace }}`\n782: - [ ] `--set workloadmanager.replicas=3` 渲染出 replicas: 3\n783: - [ ] `--set router.rbac.create=true` 渲染出 Router RBAC 资源\n784: - [ ] `--set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true` 渲染出 Volcano 全套资源\n785: - [ ] `--set-json 'imagePullSecrets=[{\"name\":\"my-secret\"}]'` 渲染出 imagePullSecrets\n786: \n787: ---\n788: \n789: ## 7. 后续变更 (Follow-up Changes)\n790: \n791: | 变更 | 依赖关系 | 说明 |\n792: |------|----------|------|\n793: | CRD YAML 自动生成 | 依赖 `make gen-crd` | 从 Go 类型 kubebuilder 标记自动生成 CRD，替代手工维护 |\n794: | Helm 单元测试 (helm-unittest) | 依赖本 AR 完成 | 引入 helm-unittest 插件，将 delta-spec 场景转为自动化测试用例 |\n795: | Helm 3 apiVersion v2 升级 | 依赖本 AR 完成 | 如需 subchart/library chart 支持，升级 apiVersion 至 v2 |\n796: | 生产级 values 覆盖文件 | 依赖本 AR 完成 | 为 staging/production 环境创建独立的 values-override.yaml |\n797: | Helm 仓库发布 | 依赖本 AR 完成 | `helm package` + `helm push` 到 OCI registry 或 ChartMuseum |\n798: | GitOps 集成 (ArgoCD/Flux) | 依赖本 AR 完成 | 将 chart 作为 HelmRepository + HelmRelease 纳入 GitOps 管理 |\n\n(End of file - total 798 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-030: Helm Chart 模板与 Values — Design/设计说明\n\n## 1. 架构 (Architecture)\n\n### 1.1 定位 (Purpose/Positioning)\n\n`manifests/charts/base` 是 AgentCube 控制面栈的 Helm Chart，提供参数化的 Kubernetes 资源模板，支持一键安装、升级和回滚。Chart 驱动 Workload Manager、Router、可选 Volcano 调度器的完整部署生命周期，通过 `values.yaml` 集中管理所有可配置参数（镜像、副本数、资源配额、Redis 连接、环境变量覆盖）。\n\nChart 是 E2E 测试、生产部署、开发者本地 Kind 集群的统一入口，消除手动编辑 YAML 的需求。\n\n### 1.2 包结构 (Package Layout)\n\n```\nmanifests/charts/base/\n├── Chart.yaml                              # Chart 元数据 (apiVersion v1, name agentcube, version 0.1.0)\n├── values.yaml                             # 默认配置值树 (Redis, Router, WorkloadManager, Volcano)\n├── crds/\n│   ├── runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_agentruntimes.yaml    # AgentRuntime CRD (v1alpha1, Namespaced)\n│   └── runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_codeinterpreters.yaml # CodeInterpreter CRD (v1alpha1, Namespaced)\n└── templates/","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-030/design.md","time":{"start":1775871001411,"end":1775871001420}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775871003063,"sessionID":"ses_285d94d8fffeNOnrGGHJVfF0qU","part":{"id":"prt_d7a2903d3001lVz5revIaRo19g","messageID":"msg_d7a28f59c001xaYdOcRgV6cI4S","sessionID":"ses_285d94d8fffeNOnrGGHJVfF0qU","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_55d13f64b5a04283b01af8e1","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-030/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-030/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-030: Helm Chart 模板与 Values — Delta Spec\n2: \n3: ## Context\n4: \n5: - **Module:** `manifests`\n6: - **Language:** YAML\n7: - **Size:** L\n8: - **Base specs:** `deployment/spec.md`, `deployment/design.md`\n9: \n10: ## Delta Requirements\n11: \n12: ### Requirement: Chart.yaml metadata\n13: \n14: The chart SHALL define `Chart.yaml` with `apiVersion: v1`, `name: agentcube`, `version: 0.1.0`, and `appVersion: 1.0.0`.\n15: \n16: #### Scenario: Chart metadata fields are correct\n17: - **GIVEN** the file `manifests/charts/base/Chart.yaml` exists\n18: - **WHEN** it is parsed as YAML\n19: - **THEN** `apiVersion` equals `v1`, `name` equals `agentcube`, `version` equals `0.1.0`, and `appVersion` equals `1.0.0`\n20: \n21: #### Scenario: Helm lint passes on chart metadata\n22: - **GIVEN** a valid `Chart.yaml` with the fields above\n23: - **WHEN** `helm lint manifests/charts/base` is run\n24: - **THEN** no errors or warnings related to chart metadata are reported\n25: \n26: ---\n27: \n28: ### Requirement: values.yaml default key tree\n29: \n30: The chart SHALL provide a `values.yaml` with the full key tree documented in the deployment design, including typed defaults for `imagePullSecrets`, `nameOverride`, `fullnameOverride`, `redis.addr`, `redis.password`, `router` (replicas, image, service, resources, config, extraEnv, serviceAccountName, rbac), `workloadmanager` (replicas, image, service, resources, extraEnv), and `volcano.scheduler` (enabled, replicas, image). Comments SHALL state that Redis settings must be provided by the user during installation.\n31: \n32: #### Scenario: Default values are valid YAML\n33: - **GIVEN** the file `manifests/charts/base/values.yaml`\n34: - **WHEN** it is parsed as YAML\n35: - **THEN** no parse errors occur and all top-level keys (`imagePullSecrets`, `nameOverride`, `fullnameOverride`, `redis`, `router`, `workloadmanager`, `volcano`) are present\n36: \n37: #### Scenario: Redis defaults are empty strings with comments\n38: - **GIVEN** `values.yaml` is rendered\n39: - **WHEN** `redis.addr` and `redis.password` are read\n40: - **THEN** both default to `\"\"` and comments indicate they must be provided at install time\n41: \n42: #### Scenario: Router defaults match design\n43: - **GIVEN** `values.yaml` is rendered\n44: - **WHEN** router values are read\n45: - **THEN** `router.replicas` is `1`, `router.image.repository` is `ghcr.io/volcano-sh/agentcube-router`, `router.image.pullPolicy` is `IfNotPresent`, `router.image.tag` is `latest`, `router.service.type` is `ClusterIP`, `router.service.port` is `8080`, `router.service.targetPort` is `8080`, resource limits are `cpu: 500m, memory: 512Mi`, requests are `cpu: 100m, memory: 128Mi`, `router.rbac.create` is `false`\n46: \n47: #### Scenario: Workload Manager defaults match design\n48: - **GIVEN** `values.yaml` is rendered\n49: - **WHEN** workloadmanager values are read\n50: - **THEN** `workloadmanager.replicas` is `1`, `workloadmanager.image.repository` is `ghcr.io/volcano-sh/workloadmanager`, `workloadmanager.image.pullPolicy` is `IfNotPresent`, `workloadmanager.image.tag` is `latest`, `workloadmanager.service.type` is `ClusterIP`, `workloadmanager.service.port` is `8080`, resource limits are `cpu: 500m, memory: 512Mi`, requests are `cpu: 100m, memory: 128Mi`\n51: \n52: #### Scenario: Volcano scheduler defaults to disabled\n53: - **GIVEN** `values.yaml` is rendered\n54: - **WHEN** `volcano.scheduler.enabled` is read\n55: - **THEN** it defaults to `false`\n56: \n57: ---\n58: \n59: ### Requirement: Workload Manager Deployment template\n60: \n61: The template `workloadmanager.yaml` SHALL render a `Deployment` named `workloadmanager` in `{{ .Release.Namespace }}` with: replicas from `workloadmanager.replicas`; container `workloadmanager` using `repository:tag` with `imagePullPolicy`; port `http` on `workloadmanager.service.port`; env vars `AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE` (fieldRef `metadata.namespace`), `REDIS_ADDR`, `REDIS_PASSWORD`, plus `workloadmanager.extraEnv`; args `--port=<port>` and `--runtime-class-name=` (empty); resource requests/limits from values; liveness probe HTTP GET `/health` (initialDelay 10s, period 10s); readiness probe HTTP GET `/health` (initialDelay 5s, period 5s); optional `imagePullSecrets`; `serviceAccountName: workloadmanager`.\n62: \n63: #### Scenario: Default deployment renders correctly\n64: - **GIVEN** default values and release namespace `agentcube`\n65: - **WHEN** `helm template test manifests/charts/base` is run\n66: - **THEN** the output contains a `Deployment` named `workloadmanager` in namespace `agentcube` with `replicas: 1`, container image `ghcr.io/volcano-sh/workloadmanager:latest`, and `imagePullPolicy: IfNotPresent`\n67: \n68: #### Scenario: Health probes are configured\n69: - **GIVEN** default values\n70: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n71: - **THEN** the Workload Manager container has liveness probe `httpGet /health` on the service port with `initialDelaySeconds: 10, periodSeconds: 10` and readiness probe `httpGet /health` with `initialDelaySeconds: 5, periodSeconds: 5`\n72: \n73: #### Scenario: Redis env vars are injected\n74: - **GIVEN** `--set redis.addr=redis.default.svc:6379 --set redis.password=secret123`\n75: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n76: - **THEN** the Workload Manager container env includes `REDIS_ADDR=redis.default.svc:6379` and `REDIS_PASSWORD=secret123`\n77: \n78: #### Scenario: AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE uses fieldRef\n79: - **GIVEN** any valid installation\n80: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n81: - **THEN** the Workload Manager container env includes `AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE` with `valueFrom.fieldRef.fieldPath: metadata.namespace`\n82: \n83: #### Scenario: extraEnv entries are appended\n84: - **GIVEN** `--set-json 'workloadmanager.extraEnv=[{\"name\":\"CUSTOM_VAR\",\"value\":\"custom-val\"}]'`\n85: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n86: - **THEN** the Workload Manager container env includes `CUSTOM_VAR=custom-val` in addition to the standard env vars\n87: \n88: #### Scenario: Container args include port and runtime-class-name\n89: - **GIVEN** `workloadmanager.service.port` is `8080`\n90: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n91: - **THEN** the container args include `--port=8080` and `--runtime-class-name=`\n92: \n93: #### Scenario: Resource requests and limits from values\n94: - **GIVEN** default values\n95: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n96: - **THEN** the container resources have `requests: {cpu: 100m, memory: 128Mi}` and `limits: {cpu: 500m, memory: 512Mi}`\n97: \n98: #### Scenario: Custom replica count\n99: - **GIVEN** `--set workloadmanager.replicas=3`\n100: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n101: - **THEN** the Deployment spec has `replicas: 3`\n102: \n103: #### Scenario: Custom image override\n104: - **GIVEN** `--set workloadmanager.image.repository=myregistry/workloadmanager --set workloadmanager.image.tag=v1.2.3`\n105: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n106: - **THEN** the container image is `myregistry/workloadmanager:v1.2.3`\n107: \n108: #### Scenario: imagePullSecrets are applied when set\n109: - **GIVEN** `--set-json 'imagePullSecrets=[{\"name\":\"my-secret\"}]'`\n110: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n111: - **THEN** the Deployment `spec.template.spec.imagePullSecrets` includes `{name: my-secret}`\n112: \n113: ---\n114: \n115: ### Requirement: Workload Manager Service template\n116: \n117: The template `workloadmanager.yaml` SHALL render a `Service` named `workloadmanager` in `{{ .Release.Namespace }}` with: `type` from `workloadmanager.service.type`; `port` and `targetPort` from `workloadmanager.service.port`; selector `app: workloadmanager`.\n118: \n119: #### Scenario: Default service renders\n120: - **GIVEN** default values\n121: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n122: - **THEN** a `Service` named `workloadmanager` exists with `type: ClusterIP`, `port: 8080`, `targetPort: 8080`, and selector `app: workloadmanager`\n123: \n124: #### Scenario: Custom service type\n125: - **GIVEN** `--set workloadmanager.service.type=NodePort`\n126: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n127: - **THEN** the Service `type` is `NodePort`\n128: \n129: ---\n130: \n131: ### Requirement: Router Deployment template\n132: \n133: The template `agentcube-router.yaml` SHALL render a `Deployment` named `agentcube-router` in `{{ .Release.Namespace }}` with: replicas from `router.replicas`; conditional `serviceAccountName` if `router.serviceAccountName` is non-empty; container `agentcube-router` using `router.image`; container port `router.service.targetPort`; env vars `AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE` (fieldRef), `REDIS_ADDR`, `REDIS_PASSWORD`, `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL=http://workloadmanager.{{ .Release.Namespace }}.svc.cluster.local:{{ workloadmanager.service.port }}`, plus `router.extraEnv`; args `--port=<targetPort>` and `--debug`; resources from values; liveness probe `/health/live` and readiness probe `/health/ready` on targetPort (initialDelay 1s, period 2s); optional `imagePullSecrets`.\n134: \n135: #### Scenario: Default router deployment renders\n136: - **GIVEN** default values and release namespace `agentcube`\n137: - **WHEN** `helm template test manifests/charts/base` is run\n138: - **THEN** the output contains a `Deployment` named `agentcube-router` in namespace `agentcube` with `replicas: 1` and image `ghcr.io/volcano-sh/agentcube-router:latest`\n139: \n140: #### Scenario: WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL resolves via in-cluster DNS\n141: - **GIVEN** release namespace `agentcube` and `workloadmanager.service.port` is `8080`\n142: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n143: - **THEN** the Router container env includes `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL=http://workloadmanager.agentcube.svc.cluster.local:8080`\n144: \n145: #### Scenario: Router health probes\n146: - **GIVEN** default values\n147: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n148: - **THEN** the Router container has liveness probe `httpGet /health/live` with `initialDelaySeconds: 1, periodSeconds: 2` and readiness probe `httpGet /health/ready` with `initialDelaySeconds: 1, periodSeconds: 2`\n149: \n150: #### Scenario: Router args include port and debug flag\n151: - **GIVEN** `router.service.targetPort` is `8080`\n152: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n153: - **THEN** the container args include `--port=8080` and `--debug`\n154: \n155: #### Scenario: Conditional serviceAccountName\n156: - **GIVEN** `--set router.serviceAccountName=agentcube-router`\n157: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n158: - **THEN** the Router Deployment `spec.template.spec.serviceAccountName` is `agentcube-router`\n159: \n160: #### Scenario: Empty serviceAccountName omits field\n161: - **GIVEN** `router.serviceAccountName` is `\"\"` (default)\n162: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n163: - **THEN** the Router Deployment does NOT set `serviceAccountName`\n164: \n165: #### Scenario: Router extraEnv entries\n166: - **GIVEN** `--set-json 'router.extraEnv=[{\"name\":\"LOG_LEVEL\",\"value\":\"debug\"}]'`\n167: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n168: - **THEN** the Router container env includes `LOG_LEVEL=debug`\n169: \n170: ---\n171: \n172: ### Requirement: Router Service template\n173: \n174: The template `agentcube-router.yaml` SHALL render a `Service` named `agentcube-router` with: `type` from `router.service.type`; `port` from `router.service.port`; `targetPort` from `router.service.targetPort`; selector `app: agentcube-router`.\n175: \n176: #### Scenario: Default router service renders\n177: - **GIVEN** default values\n178: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n179: - **THEN** a `Service` named `agentcube-router` exists with `type: ClusterIP`, `port: 8080`, `targetPort: 8080`, and selector `app: agentcube-router`\n180: \n181: ---\n182: \n183: ### Requirement: Workload Manager RBAC template\n184: \n185: The template `rbac/workloadmanager.yaml` SHALL always render: a `ServiceAccount` named `workloadmanager` in the release namespace; a `ClusterRole` named `workloadmanager` with rules for agent-sandbox CRDs (`agents.x-k8s.io/sandboxes`, `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io/sandboxclaims`, `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io/sandboxtemplates`, `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io/sandboxwarmpools`, `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io/sandboxwarmpools/status`), AgentCube CRDs (`runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/codeinterpreters`, `codeinterpreters/status`, `codeinterpreters/finalizers`, `agentruntimes`, `agentruntimes/status`), core resources (`pods`, `secrets`), and auth (`authentication.k8s.io/tokenreviews`); a `ClusterRoleBinding` named `workloadmanager` binding the ClusterRole to the ServiceAccount in the release namespace.\n186: \n187: #### Scenario: ServiceAccount renders in release namespace\n188: - **GIVEN** release namespace `agentcube`\n189: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n190: - **THEN** a `ServiceAccount` named `workloadmanager` exists in namespace `agentcube`\n191: \n192: #### Scenario: ClusterRole grants sandbox CRD permissions\n193: - **GIVEN** any valid installation\n194: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n195: - **THEN** the `ClusterRole/workloadmanager` includes rules granting `get,list,watch,create,update,patch,delete` on `sandboxes` in `agents.x-k8s.io`\n196: \n197: #### Scenario: ClusterRole grants AgentCube CRD permissions\n198: - **GIVEN** any valid installation\n199: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n200: - **THEN** the `ClusterRole/workloadmanager` includes rules granting `get,list,watch,create,update,patch,delete` on `codeinterpreters` in `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` and `get,list,watch` on `agentruntimes` in `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`\n201: \n202: #### Scenario: ClusterRole grants status and finalizer permissions\n203: - **GIVEN** any valid installation\n204: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n205: - **THEN** the ClusterRole includes `get,update,patch` on `codeinterpreters/status`, `update` on `codeinterpreters/finalizers`, and `update,patch` on `agentruntimes/status`\n206: \n207: #### Scenario: ClusterRole grants secrets and tokenreview permissions\n208: - **GIVEN** any valid installation\n209: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n210: - **THEN** the ClusterRole includes full verbs on `secrets` in core API group and `create` on `tokenreviews` in `authentication.k8s.io`\n211: \n212: #### Scenario: ClusterRoleBinding ties SA to ClusterRole\n213: - **GIVEN** release namespace `agentcube`\n214: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n215: - **THEN** `ClusterRoleBinding/workloadmanager` has subject `ServiceAccount/workloadmanager` in namespace `agentcube` and roleRef `ClusterRole/workloadmanager`\n216: \n217: ---\n218: \n219: ### Requirement: Optional Router RBAC template\n220: \n221: The template `rbac-router.yaml` SHALL render **only if** `router.rbac.create` is true. When rendered, it SHALL create: a `ServiceAccount` named `{{ router.serviceAccountName | default \"agentcube-router\" }}` in the release namespace; a `Role` with the same name granting full verbs (`get,list,watch,create,update,patch,delete`) on `secrets` in the release namespace; a `RoleBinding` binding the Role to the ServiceAccount.\n222: \n223: #### Scenario: Router RBAC off by default\n224: - **GIVEN** `router.rbac.create: false` (default)\n225: - **WHEN** `helm template test manifests/charts/base` is run\n226: - **THEN** no Router ServiceAccount, Role, or RoleBinding resources appear in the output\n227: \n228: #### Scenario: Router RBAC enabled\n229: - **GIVEN** `--set router.rbac.create=true`\n230: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n231: - **THEN** the output contains a `ServiceAccount`, `Role`, and `RoleBinding` for the Router, all named `agentcube-router` (default)\n232: \n233: #### Scenario: Router RBAC with custom serviceAccountName\n234: - **GIVEN** `--set router.rbac.create=true --set router.serviceAccountName=my-router-sa`\n235: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n236: - **THEN** the ServiceAccount, Role, and RoleBinding are all named `my-router-sa`\n237: \n238: #### Scenario: Router Role grants secret management\n239: - **GIVEN** `--set router.rbac.create=true`\n240: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n241: - **THEN** the Router Role includes rule: apiGroup `\"\"`, resources `secrets`, verbs `get,list,watch,create,update,patch,delete`\n242: \n243: ---\n244: \n245: ### Requirement: Optional Volcano agent scheduler template\n246: \n247: The template `volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml` SHALL render **only if** `volcano.scheduler.enabled` is true. When rendered, it SHALL create (in order): `ServiceAccount/volcano-agent-scheduler`; `ConfigMap/volcano-agent-scheduler-configmap` with key `agent-scheduler.conf` (actions `allocate`, tiers with predicates and nodeorder); `ClusterRole/volcano-agent-scheduler` with the full rule set from the deployment design; `ClusterRoleBinding/volcano-agent-scheduler-role`; `Service/volcano-agent-scheduler-service` (port 8080, metrics annotations); `Deployment/volcano-agent-scheduler` with replicas from `volcano.scheduler.replicas`, image from `volcano.scheduler.image`, args including `--scheduler-name=agent-scheduler`, security contexts, and volumes for config + emptyDir.\n248: \n249: #### Scenario: Volcano scheduler disabled by default\n250: - **GIVEN** `volcano.scheduler.enabled: false` (default)\n251: - **WHEN** `helm template test manifests/charts/base` is run\n252: - **THEN** no Volcano scheduler resources appear in the output\n253: \n254: #### Scenario: Volcano scheduler enabled\n255: - **GIVEN** `--set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true`\n256: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n257: - **THEN** the output contains ServiceAccount, ConfigMap, ClusterRole, ClusterRoleBinding, Service, and Deployment for the Volcano scheduler\n258: \n259: #### Scenario: Volcano ConfigMap contains scheduler config\n260: - **GIVEN** `--set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true`\n261: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n262: - **THEN** `ConfigMap/volcano-agent-scheduler-configmap` has key `agent-scheduler.conf` containing actions `allocate` and tiers with `predicates` and `nodeorder`\n263: \n264: #### Scenario: Volcano Deployment uses values for replicas and image\n265: - **GIVEN** `--set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true --set volcano.scheduler.replicas=2 --set volcano.scheduler.image.tag=v1.0.0`\n266: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n267: - **THEN** the Volcano Deployment has `replicas: 2` and image `ghcr.io/volcano-sh/vc-agent-scheduler:v1.0.0`\n268: \n269: #### Scenario: Volcano Deployment args include scheduler name\n270: - **GIVEN** `--set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true`\n271: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n272: - **THEN** the Volcano container args include `--scheduler-name=agent-scheduler`\n273: \n274: #### Scenario: Volcano Service has metrics annotations\n275: - **GIVEN** `--set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true`\n276: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n277: - **THEN** `Service/volcano-agent-scheduler-service` has port `8080` and Prometheus metrics annotations\n278: \n279: ---\n280: \n281: ### Requirement: CRDs shipped with chart\n282: \n283: The chart SHALL ship `CustomResourceDefinition` manifests under `crds/` directory: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_agentruntimes.yaml` and `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_codeinterpreters.yaml`. Both SHALL use API group `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`, version `v1alpha1` (served and storage), and `scope: Namespaced`.\n284: \n285: #### Scenario: AgentRuntime CRD is present\n286: - **GIVEN** the chart directory `manifests/charts/base/crds/`\n287: - **WHEN** `helm template test manifests/charts/base --include-crds` is run\n288: - **THEN** the output contains `CustomResourceDefinition/agentruntimes.runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` with `spec.group: runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`, `spec.versions` including `v1alpha1` as served and storage, and `scope: Namespaced`\n289: \n290: #### Scenario: CodeInterpreter CRD is present\n291: - **GIVEN** the chart directory `manifests/charts/base/crds/`\n292: - **WHEN** `helm template test manifests/charts/base --include-crds` is run\n293: - **THEN** the output contains `CustomResourceDefinition/codeinterpreters.runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` with `spec.group: runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`, `spec.versions` including `v1alpha1` as served and storage, and `scope: Namespaced`\n294: \n295: #### Scenario: AgentRuntime CRD required spec fields\n296: - **GIVEN** the AgentRuntime CRD YAML\n297: - **WHEN** its `openAPIV3Schema` is inspected\n298: - **THEN** `spec.required` includes `maxSessionDuration`, `podTemplate`, `sessionTimeout`, and `targetPort`\n299: \n300: #### Scenario: CodeInterpreter CRD required spec fields\n301: - **GIVEN** the CodeInterpreter CRD YAML\n302: - **WHEN** its `openAPIV3Schema` is inspected\n303: - **THEN** `spec.required` includes `template` and `spec.authMode` defaults to `picod`\n304: \n305: ---\n306: \n307: ### Requirement: Helm install command with required values\n308: \n309: The chart SHALL support installation via `helm upgrade --install <release> manifests/charts/base --namespace <ns> --create-namespace` with `--set redis.addr=...` and optional `--set redis.password=...`. All component workloads SHALL render without manual editing of the output YAML.\n310: \n311: #### Scenario: Install with minimal required values\n312: - **GIVEN** a Kubernetes cluster with Helm 3\n313: - **WHEN** `helm upgrade --install agentcube manifests/charts/base --namespace agentcube --create-namespace --set redis.addr=redis.agentcube.svc:6379 --set redis.password=pass --wait` succeeds\n314: - **THEN** Deployments `workloadmanager` and `agentcube-router`, Services, RBAC, and CRDs are all created in namespace `agentcube`\n315: \n316: #### Scenario: Install with component image overrides\n317: - **GIVEN** local images loaded into a Kind cluster\n318: - **WHEN** `helm upgrade --install agentcube manifests/charts/base --namespace agentcube --create-namespace --set redis.addr=redis.agentcube.svc:6379 --set redis.password=\"\" --set workloadmanager.image.repository=workloadmanager --set workloadmanager.image.tag=latest --set router.image.repository=agentcube-router --set router.image.tag=latest --wait` succeeds\n319: - **THEN** Workload Manager and Router Deployments use the local image names and tags\n320: \n321: #### Scenario: Install with router RBAC and extraEnv\n322: - **GIVEN** a cluster with Helm 3\n323: - **WHEN** install includes `--set router.rbac.create=true --set router.serviceAccountName=agentcube-router --set-json 'router.extraEnv=[{\"name\":\"REDIS_PASSWORD_REQUIRED\",\"value\":\"false\"}]'`\n324: - **THEN** Router RBAC resources are created and Router pods have the specified extraEnv\n325: \n326: ---\n327: \n328: ### Requirement: Helm upgrade preserves state\n329: \n330: The chart SHALL support upgrading an existing release with modified values without deleting existing resources (except where Helm's native upgrade semantics dictate replacement).\n331: \n332: #### Scenario: Upgrade replica count\n333: - **GIVEN** a release installed with default values (1 replica for Workload Manager)\n334: - **WHEN** `helm upgrade` is run with `--set workloadmanager.replicas=3`\n335: - **THEN** the Workload Manager Deployment is updated to `replicas: 3` without downtime (rolling update)\n336: \n337: #### Scenario: Upgrade image tag\n338: - **GIVEN** a release installed with `workloadmanager.image.tag=latest`\n339: - **WHEN** `helm upgrade` is run with `--set workloadmanager.image.tag=v1.1.0`\n340: - **THEN** the Workload Manager Deployment image is updated to `ghcr.io/volcano-sh/workloadmanager:v1.1.0`\n341: \n342: ---\n343: \n344: ### Requirement: Helm template dry-run produces valid Kubernetes manifests\n345: \n346: The chart SHALL produce valid Kubernetes YAML when rendered with `helm template`, with no unresolved template variables and all required fields populated from defaults or overrides.\n347: \n348: #### Scenario: Default template output is valid\n349: - **GIVEN** default values\n350: - **WHEN** `helm template test manifests/charts/base` is piped to `kubectl apply --dry-run=client -f -`\n351: - **THEN** no validation errors are reported\n352: \n353: #### Scenario: Template with all overrides is valid\n354: - **GIVEN** `--set redis.addr=redis.ns.svc:6379 --set redis.password=secret --set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true --set router.rbac.create=true`\n355: - **WHEN** `helm template test manifests/charts/base` is piped to `kubectl apply --dry-run=client -f -`\n356: - **THEN** no validation errors are reported\n357: \n358: ---\n359: \n360: ### Requirement: Namespace scoping via Release.Namespace\n361: \n362: All namespaced resources SHALL use `{{ .Release.Namespace }}` for their namespace field, not hardcoded values.\n363: \n364: #### Scenario: Workload Manager Deployment uses release namespace\n365: - **GIVEN** `--namespace production`\n366: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n367: - **THEN** the Workload Manager Deployment has `metadata.namespace: production`\n368: \n369: #### Scenario: Router Service uses release namespace\n370: - **GIVEN** `--namespace staging`\n371: - **WHEN` templates are rendered\n372: - **THEN** the Router Service has `metadata.namespace: staging`\n373: \n374: ---\n375: \n376: ### Requirement: nameOverride and fullnameOverride support\n377: \n378: The chart SHALL support `nameOverride` and `fullnameOverride` values for customizing resource names, following Helm naming conventions.\n379: \n380: #### Scenario: Default naming convention\n381: - **GIVEN** default values and release name `my-release`\n382: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n383: - **THEN** resource names follow the chart's default naming (e.g., `workloadmanager`, `agentcube-router`)\n384: \n385: #### Scenario: fullnameOverride renames resources\n386: - **GIVEN** `--set fullnameOverride=agentcube-prod`\n387: - **WHEN** templates are rendered\n388: - **THEN** applicable resource names use `agentcube-prod` as the base name\n389: \n390: ## File Changes\n391: \n392: | Action | File | Description |\n393: |--------|------|-------------|\n394: | Create | `manifests/charts/base/Chart.yaml` | Chart metadata (apiVersion v1, name agentcube, version 0.1.0, appVersion 1.0.0) |\n395: | Create | `manifests/charts/base/values.yaml` | Default configuration values for all components (Redis, Router, Workload Manager, Volcano) |\n396: | Create | `manifests/charts/base/templates/workloadmanager.yaml` | Workload Manager Deployment + Service with health probes, Redis env vars, extraEnv |\n397: | Create | `manifests/charts/base/templates/agentcube-router.yaml` | Router Deployment + Service with health probes, WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL, conditional serviceAccountName |\n398: | Create | `manifests/charts/base/templates/rbac/workloadmanager.yaml` | Workload Manager ServiceAccount + ClusterRole + ClusterRoleBinding |\n399: | Create | `manifests/charts/base/templates/rbac-router.yaml` | Optional Router ServiceAccount + Role + RoleBinding (gated by router.rbac.create) |\n400: | Create | `manifests/charts/base/templates/volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml` | Optional Volcano scheduler resources (gated by volcano.scheduler.enabled) |\n401: | Create | `manifests/charts/base/crds/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_agentruntimes.yaml` | AgentRuntime CRD (group runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh, v1alpha1, Namespaced) |\n402: | Create | `manifests/charts/base/crds/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_codeinterpreters.yaml` | CodeInterpreter CRD (group runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh, v1alpha1, Namespaced) |\n\n(End of file - total 402 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-030: Helm Chart 模板与 Values — Delta Spec\n\n## Context\n\n- **Module:** `manifests`\n- **Language:** YAML\n- **Size:** L\n- **Base specs:** `deployment/spec.md`, `deployment/design.md`\n\n## Delta Requirements\n\n### Requirement: Chart.yaml metadata\n\nThe chart SHALL define `Chart.yaml` with `apiVersion: v1`, `name: agentcube`, `version: 0.1.0`, and `appVersion: 1.0.0`.\n\n#### Scenario: Chart metadata fields are correct\n- **GIVEN** the file `manifests/charts/base/Chart.yaml` exists\n- **WHEN** it is parsed as YAML\n- **THEN** `apiVersion` equals `v1`, `name` equals `agentcube`, `version` equals `0.1.0`, and `appVersion` equals `1.0.0`\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-030/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775871003051,"end":1775871003060}}}}
