{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775871005484,"sessionID":"ses_285d94d8fffeNOnrGGHJVfF0qU","part":{"id":"prt_d7a290e38001yKCY0O4svpkb3F","messageID":"msg_d7a28f59c001xaYdOcRgV6cI4S","sessionID":"ses_285d94d8fffeNOnrGGHJVfF0qU","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_7509efc6070a406d9ab7850c","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-001/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-001/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-001 任务清单\n2: \n3: > **Stage**: ST-4 (Implementation)\n4: > **Module**: `pkg/apis`\n5: > **Language**: Go\n6: > **Size**: S\n7: \n8: ---\n9: \n10: ## T-001: 创建 pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1 目录结构\n11: \n12: - [ ] T-001.01 创建目录 `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n13: - [ ] T-001.02 确认 `go.mod` 中 `k8s.io/api`、`k8s.io/apimachinery`、`sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime` 依赖版本正确（v0.34.1 / v0.22.2）\n14: \n15: **验收**: 目录存在；`go mod tidy` 无报错\n16: \n17: ---\n18: \n19: ## T-002: 创建 doc.go — 包声明与代码生成标记\n20: \n21: - [ ] T-002.01 创建 `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/doc.go`\n22: - [ ] T-002.02 包含 `// +k8s:deepcopy-gen=package` 标记\n23: - [ ] T-002.03 包含 `// +groupName=runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` 标记\n24: - [ ] T-002.04 包名为 `v1alpha1`\n25: \n26: **验收**: `go build ./pkg/apis/...` 编译通过\n27: \n28: ---\n29: \n30: ## T-003: 创建 groupversion_info.go — GroupVersion 与 SchemeBuilder\n31: \n32: - [ ] T-003.01 定义 `GroupVersion = schema.GroupVersion{Group: \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\", Version: \"v1alpha1\"}`\n33: - [ ] T-003.02 定义 `SchemeBuilder = &scheme.Builder{GroupVersion: GroupVersion}`\n34: - [ ] T-003.03 定义 `AddToScheme = SchemeBuilder.AddToScheme`\n35: - [ ] T-003.04 导入 `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime/schema`\n36: - [ ] T-003.05 导入 `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/scheme`\n37: \n38: **验收**: `go build ./pkg/apis/...` 编译通过；`GroupVersion.Group == \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\